Sentence: Among various IBS materials, the 122-type AEFe 2 As 2 (AE = Ba, Sr) are studied as most promising candidates for high-performance superconducting wires and tapes, since they have high transition temperature, T c , (â¼38 K) for bulk , very high upper critical field, H c2 (> 500 kOe) , and relatively small anisotropy (Î³ < 2) .
